WEBVTT

00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:03.360
I want to share with you

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.040
a moment in my life

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:12.800
when the hurt and wounds of racism

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:18.320
were both deadly and paralyzing for me.

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:22.200
And I think what I've learned

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:27.400
can be a source of healing for all of us.

